{"tid":2214482,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"全球身價最高球隊是……","createTime":"2020-09-23T09:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T15:13:29.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ae1e9355578bafc8ebecbe162947e6ac280d5705","tid":2214482,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:36:35.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】根據德國《轉會市場》統計顯示，全球只有3支球隊的身價超過9億鎊，哪一隊排名榜首？<br />\n<br />\n隨著艾簡達拿（Thiago Alcantara）和迪奧高祖達加盟，上季英超冠軍利物浦成為全球身價最高球隊。紅軍以9.867億鎊獨佔鰲頭，較次席的曼城高出5000多萬鎊，要留意的是，這可不是轉會費數字，而是《轉會市場》的估計身價。 「埃及文明」沙拿和沙迪奧文尼雙雙超過1億鎊，阿歷山大阿奴達到9900萬鎊，另有5人超過5000萬鎊。全球只有3支球隊身價突破9億鎊，曼城以9.33億鎊屈居次席，巴塞隆拿以9.1億鎊排名第3。車路士以8.26億鎊排名第4，曼聯以7.195億鎊排名第7，熱刺是前10位中第5支英超球隊。 另外，皇家馬德里以7.9億鎊排名第5，歐聯冠軍拜仁慕尼黑排名第6，身價7.54億鎊。"},{"pid":"998d007fff75c7201f4343d3220ad3ceb6f6fe8c","tid":2214482,"uid":72497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:39:04.000Z","msg":"巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc95d076301eee7cb359c78bc1ed15486b73b56d","tid":2214482,"uid":220431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:39:16.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿以9.1億鎊排名第3<br />\n呢隊垃圾波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031fa36d03505a8687b307500b51c636c960e0a5","tid":2214482,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"998d007fff75c7201f4343d3220ad3ceb6f6fe8c","tid":2214482,"uid":72497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:39:04.000Z","msg":"巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:40:09.000Z","msg":"美斯=2億"},{"pid":"56e582cb5b0b684b33d460696a14e8292f2c8b21","tid":2214482,"uid":50041,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"031fa36d03505a8687b307500b51c636c960e0a5","